deviates only a little from truth in the beginning is led farther and farther afield in the sequel, and to errors which are a thousand times as large.&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Source:&nbsp;<\/em><a href=\"http:\/\/www.cscd.osaka-u.ac.jp\/user\/rosaldo\/FBrentano_Aristotle_Being1862-1975.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><em>On the Several Senses of Being in Aristotle&nbsp;<\/em><\/a><em>\u200b<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-1-question-for-you\">1 QUESTION FOR YOU<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>What 6-month period of your life was the most energizing and fun?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>What can you learn from your answer?<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p id=\"h-until-next-week\">Until next week,<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>James Clear<br>\u200b<em>Author of the million-copy bestseller,\u00a0<\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/atomichabits.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><em>Atomic Habits<\/em><\/a><em>\u200b<br>Creator of the\u00a0<\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.com\/habit-journal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><em>Habit Journal<\/em><\/a><em>\u200b<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>3 IDEAS FROM ME I. &#8220;Repetition unlocks value. The value of your first workout increases the more you exercise. The value of your first article increases the more you write. The value of your first conversation increases the longer you stay in the relationship. Day One continues to compound.&#8221; \u200bII. &#8220;The sooner you make a [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"menu_order":0,"template":"","acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v20.5 (Yoast SEO v20.6) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>3-2-1: On allowing yourself to be happy and full, and how small errors compound - James Clear<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/jamescl